%sql
drop table if exists AIRLINE_SIMULATION;

create table AIRLINE_SIMULATION
(
ID LONG NOT NULL,
Year INTEGER NOT NULL,
Month INTEGER NOT NULL,
DayofMonth INTEGER NOT NULL,
DayOfWeek INTEGER NOT NULL,
DepTime INTEGER,
CRSDepTime INTEGER,
ArrTime INTEGER,
CRSArrTime INTEGER,
UniqueCarrier VARCHAR(25),
FlightNum INTEGER,
TailNum VARCHAR(25),
ActualElapsedTime INTEGER,
CRSElapsedTime INTEGER,
AirTime INTEGER,
ArrDelay INTEGER,
DepDelay INTEGER,
Origin VARCHAR(25),
Dest VARCHAR(25),
Distance INTEGER,
TaxiIn INTEGER,
TaxiOut INTEGER,
Cancelled INTEGER,
CancellationCode VARCHAR(25),
Diverted INTEGER,
CarrierDelay INTEGER,
WeatherDelay INTEGER,
NASDelay INTEGER,
SecurityDelay INTEGER,
LateAircraftDelay INTEGER
)
 USING COLUMN OPTIONS (PARTITION_BY 'UNIQUECARRIER') AS SELECT * FROM AIRLINE_CSV;

%sql
SELECT * FROM AIRLINE_SIMULATION LIMIT 100;

%sql
CREATE TABLE FHIR_ORIGINAL.observations
(
ID LONG NOT NULL,
DATE DATE NOT NULL,
PATIENT VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
ENCOUNTER VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
CODE VARCHAR(20),
DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(100),
VALUE DOUBLE,
UNITS VARCHAR(10),
TYPE VARCHAR(20)
)
using column options(PARTITION_BY 'PATIENT', buckets '12') as (select * from FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_observations);

CREATE TABLE FHIR_ORIGINAL.procedures
(
ID LONG NOT NULL,
DATE DATE NOT NULL,
PATIENT VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
ENCOUNTER VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
CODE VARCHAR(20),
DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(50),
COST DOUBLE,
REASONCODE VARCHAR(10),
REASONDESCRIPTION VARCHAR(100)
)
using column options(PARTITION_BY 'PATIENT', buckets '12') as (select * from FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_procedures);

%sql
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.observations_archive;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.observations_simulation;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.procedures_archive;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.procedures_simulation;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.observations;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.procedures;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_observations;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_procedures;
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_observations USING csv OPTIONS (path '../../data/FHIR/csv/observations_withID.csv'); 
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE FHIR_ORIGINAL.staging_procedures USING csv OPTIONS (path '../../data/FHIR/csv/procedures_withID.csv');

(
